{"type": "article", "id": 14654, "title": "白瓷杯", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-09T07:27:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000316zCaRhfAQluOgPVij.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款白色的瓷杯来自荷兰赞德福特的工作室，是由 3D 打印技术铸造，再进入窑子烧制的。它的表面呈现出并不规则的三角形，像是瓷杯的肌理，有微妙的触感。杯子并不是纯粹的白色，似乎透着淡淡的蓝，令人联想到云朵。瓷杯有大小两款，分别售价 24 欧和 22 欧，都带有一个茶托，使用时有更多的功能。<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/in-the-clouds-cup-m-saucer/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142121ATNha32Ucpk0DWCO.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"940\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142122LpnKWVf8eGmd5C3Y.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"940\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142122kd4t5x8MDlS1CFUE.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"940\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}